'''''Changes & Things''''' is an album by bassist and cellist [[Sam Jones (musician)|Sam Jones]] which was recorded in 1977 and released on the [[Xanadu Records|Xanadu]] label.<ref>[http://www.jazzlists.com/SJ_Label_Xanadu.htm Xanadu Records discography] accessed April 28, 2014</ref>

==Reception==
{{Album ratings
| rev1 = [[AllMusic]]
| rev1Score = {{rating|4|5}}<ref name="Allmusic"/> 
}}
[[Scott Yanow]] of [[AllMusic]] states "Bassist Sam Jones' recordings as a leader have generally been underrated, but virtually every one is well-planned and recommended... The solos are colorful and purposeful, the material fairly diverse, and the results consistently swinging yet rarely predictable".<ref name="Allmusic">Yanow, S., [http://www.allmusic.com/album/changes-things-mw0001879779 Allmusic Review] accessed April 28, 2014</ref>

== Track listing ==
''All compositions by Sam Jones except as indicated''
