# "Miss Morgan" - 7:59  
# "Laverne Walk" ([[Oscar Pettiford]]) -  5:22  
# "Trane Changes" (Slide Hampton) - 7:29  
# "Sam's Things" - 5:57  
# "Blue's" (Blue Mitchell) - 7:58

